        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for CD’s answers on <hi rend="italic">Passiflora</hi></p> 
            <p>and Asa Gray review.</p> 
<p>Has observed gradation of sterility in <hi rend="italic">Oncidium</hi> species.</p>  
<p>Has observed rostellar germination and fertilisation in <hi rend="italic">Laelia</hi>. The latter was prevented in <hi rend="italic">Bletia</hi> by covering the stigma with plaster of Paris.</p>  
<p><hi rend="italic">Gongora atropurpurea</hi> capsules are swelling.</p> 
        </abstract>
